The paper deals with the problem of image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed algorithm involves creating a model based on user input, which suggests a possible connection to graphics (cs.GR). The use of attributed relational graphs and appearance features suggests a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the optimization aspect of the algorithm suggests a possible connection to machine learning (cs.LG).
